<p><span class="bold">Operation: Wet ...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="kbw65y" data-video-descrip="Murray and Bently break into the watertower and shut-down the plaza fountain. Sly pickpockets the repair truck keys from the repair man Dimitris sends and Murray and Bentley use them to steal the repair truck. Sly climbs to the top of the nightclub's peacock sign and catches the winch-line and attaches it to the sign. They pull the sing down and smash it over the fountain, creating a hole into Dimitri's printing-press room where the tail-feathers are located." data-video-title="Operation: Thunder Beak" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/kbw65y_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/kbw65y.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/OperationBlank" data-video-tropename="Operation: [Blank]" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/Sly2BandOfThieves,Recap/Sly2BandOfThievesMission01TheBlackChateau" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/kbw65y.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Operation: Thun...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="5fv0eo" data-video-descrip="Bentley demolishes the palace's main bridge to prevent reinforcements from arriving and distract the guards already guarding the wings. Sly dances with Carmelita as a distraction so that Murray can steal the wings. Bentley uses his chopper to protect Murray till he makes it to the van and they escape." data-video-title="Operation: Hippo Drop" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/5fv0eo_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/5fv0eo.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/OperationBlank" data-video-tropename="Operation: [Blank]" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/Sly2BandOfThievesMission02AStarryEyedEncounter,VideoGame/Sly2BandOfThieves" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/5fv0eo.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Operation: Hipp...</span></p>
</a>
