<div id="_pm_videoViewer" class="full-screen">
<a href="#close" class="close" id="_pm_videoViewer-close"></a>
<div class="_pmvv-body">
<div class="_pmvv-vidbox">
<video id='overlay-video-player-box' data-video-id="py4juc" class='video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-16-9'>
</video>
<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Operation: Reverse Double-Cros</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Cooper Gang's ship battling LeFwee's ship The Death's Head. Since Penelope might be on-board, they can't sink it. Instead, Sly boards the boat and &quot;surrenders&quot; to get a proper audience with LeFwee and find out where he is keeping Penelope.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="py4juc">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
<p>How well does it match the trope?</p>
<div id="star-rating-group">
<div class="trope-rate">
<input type="radio" id="lamp5" name="rate" value="5" />
<label for="lamp5" title="Absolutely"></label>
